No. 10A785. Martin Link, Applicant v. George A. Lombardi, Director, Missouri Department of Corrections, et al. 562 U.S. 1208, 131 S. Ct. 1464,

179 L. Ed. 2d 91,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 1076. February 8, 2011.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death, presented to Justice Alito and by him referred to the Court, denied.
